=begin pod
=TITLE Gnome::Gtk4::R-FontChooser
=head1 Description

L<Gnome::Gtk4::R-FontChooser|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/R-FontChooser> is an interface that can be implemented by widgets
for choosing fonts.

In GTK, the main objects that implement this interface are
L<Gnome::Gtk4::FontChooserWidget|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/FontChooserWidget>, L<Gnome::Gtk4::FontChooserDialog|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/FontChooserDialog> and
L<Gnome::Gtk4::FontButton|/content-docs/api2/reference/Gtk4/FontButton>.

