=begin pod
=head1 Signals

=comment -----------------------------------------------------------------------
=head3 font-activated

Emitted when a font is activated.

This usually happens when the user double clicks an item,
or an item is selected and the user presses one of the keys
Space, Shift+Space, Return or Enter.

=begin code
method handler (
  Str $fontname,
  Int :$_handle_id,
  N-GObject :$_native-object,
  Gnome::Gtk4::FontChooser :$_widget,
  *%user-options
)
=end code

=item $fontname; the font name.
=item $_handle_id; The registered event handler id.
=item $_native-object; The native object provided by the Raku object which registered this event. This is a native B<Gnome::Gtk4::FontChooser> object.
=item %user-options; A list of named arguments provided by L<.register-signal() in class Object|/content-docs/api2/reference/GObject/Object#register-signal>.

